- Compilation and Installation

Invoke make in this directory to create the executable
file qbe.  Install using 'make install', the standard
DESTDIR and PREFIX environment variables are supported.
Alternatively, you may simply copy the qbe binary manually.

make
Bsp. zum anzeigen von Assembly. ./tools/genasm test/echo.ssa /Users/lucadoll/Desktop/LBS-Compiler/qbe-1.2/result/echo.s

Canaries an: 
cd /Users/lucadoll/Desktop/LBS-Compiler/qbe-1.2
make clean
make CANARY=1 qbe
cp -f qbe result/qbe.canary

Canaries aus: 
make clean
make CANARY=0 qbe
cp -f qbe result/qbe.no_canary

Kompilieren (direkter Vergleich):
./result/qbe.canary -o result/stack_canary_attack.canary.s demo/stack_canary_attack.ssa
./result/qbe.no_canary -o result/stack_canary_attack.no_canary.s demo/stack_canary_attack.ssa

NOP Insert:
./qbe --diversify --div-nop=35 --div-seed=7 -o result/nop_insert_demo.div.s test/_nop_insert_demo.ssa
./qbe -o result/nop_insert_demo.base.s test/_nop_insert_demo.ssa
diff -u result/nop_insert_demo.base.s result/nop_insert_demo.div.s
rg -n '^\tnop$' result/nop_insert_demo.div.s

No NOP Insert:
./qbe --diversify --div-nop=35 --no-div-nop -o /tmp/nop.off.s test/_nop_insert_demo.ssa
cmp -s result/nop_insert_demo.base.s /tmp/nop.off.s && echo identical

Register Assignment Randomization:
./qbe --diversify --div-regrand --div-seed=7 -o result/regrand_demo.div.s test/_regrand_demo.ssa
./qbe -o result/regrand_demo.base.s test/_regrand_demo.ssa
diff -u result/regrand_demo.base.s result/regrand_demo.div.s

No Register Randomization:
./qbe --diversify --div-regrand --div-seed=7 -o result/regrand_demo.div.s test/_regrand_demo.ssa
./qbe -o result/regrand_demo.base.s test/_regrand_demo.ssa
diff -u result/regrand_demo.base.s result/regrand_demo.div.s

Function Permutation:
./qbe -o result/funcperm_demo.base.s test/_funcperm_demo.ssa
./qbe --diversify --div-funcperm --div-seed=7 -o result/funcperm_demo.seed7.s test/_funcperm_demo.ssa
./qbe --diversify --div-funcperm --div-seed=8 -o result/funcperm_demo.seed8.s test/_funcperm_demo.ssa
rg -n '^\.globl ' result/funcperm_demo.base.s result/funcperm_demo.seed7.s result/funcperm_demo.seed8.s
diff -u result/funcperm_demo.base.s result/funcperm_demo.seed7.s | sed -n '1,120p'

No Function Permutation:
./qbe --diversify --div-funcperm --div-seed=7 --no-div-funcperm -o /tmp/funcperm.off.s test/_funcperm_demo.ssa
cmp -s result/funcperm_demo.base.s /tmp/funcperm.off.s && echo identical

Gleicher Seed / anderer Seed:
./qbe --diversify --div-funcperm --div-seed=7 -o /tmp/f1.s test/_funcperm_demo.ssa
./qbe --diversify --div-funcperm --div-seed=7 -o /tmp/f2.s test/_funcperm_demo.ssa
cmp -s /tmp/f1.s /tmp/f2.s && echo identical

./qbe --diversify --div-funcperm --div-seed=8 -o /tmp/f3.s test/_funcperm_demo.ssa
cmp -s /tmp/f1.s /tmp/f3.s || echo different

All together: 
cc result/nop_insert_demo.base.s -o /tmp/nop_base
cc result/nop_insert_demo.div.s -o /tmp/nop_div

cc result/regrand_demo.base.s -o /tmp/regrand_base
cc result/regrand_demo.div.s -o /tmp/regrand_div
/tmp/regrand_base; echo $?
/tmp/regrand_div; echo $?

cc result/funcperm_demo.base.s -o /tmp/funcperm_base
cc result/funcperm_demo.seed7.s -o /tmp/funcperm_seed7
/tmp/funcperm_base; echo $?
/tmp/funcperm_seed7; echo $?


